org.eclipse.eef

Interface EEFCustomWidgetDescription

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EEFControlDescription, EEFWidgetDescription, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EEFCustomWidgetDescriptionImpl

    public interface EEFCustomWidgetDescription
extends EEFWidgetDescription
    A representation of the model object 'EEF Custom Widget Description'. Represents a custom widget in the user interface.

    The following features are supported:

    • Custom Expressions
    • Style
    • Conditional Styles
    See Also:
    EefPackage.getEEFCustomWidgetDescription()
